## Time-Sensitive Content

### Deadlines

```yaml
---
$deadline = "2026-03-31"
$date_format = "DD MMMM YYYY"
---
```

**Deadline:** {$deadline}

:::if {$created > {$deadline}}
:::error [Overdue]
This document is past the deadline!
:::
:::

### Maintenance Windows

```yaml
---
$maintenance = "2026-02-20 02:00"
$datetime_format = "YYYY-MM-DD HH:mm"
---
```

**Next Maintenance:** {$maintenance}

